             was indicted for <rs id="t18311201-274-off1457" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18311201-274-off1457" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18311201-274-off1457" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18311201-274-cd1458" type="crimeDate">2nd of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18311201-274-off1457 t18311201-274-cd1458"></join>, 5 sovereigns, 2 half-crowns, and 3 sixpences, the monies of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18311201-274-victim2071" type="victimName">
                           Matthew 
                           Rutherford
                        <interp inst="t18311201-274-victim2071" type="surname" value="Rutherford"></interp>
